Stallergenes Says Gradnik Will Become CEO From Jan. 1, 2012

-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 
2011-10-03T16:54:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/stallergenes-says-gradnik-will-become-ceo-from-jan-1-2012.html
Stallergenes named Roberto Gradnik as
deputy chief executive officer and said he will become CEO from
Jan. 1, 2012.  Current Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Albert Saporta
will become non-executive chairman from the same date at his own
request, the company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steve Rhinds at 
 srhinds@bloomberg.net  